      <title>瑞银完成历史性收购，瑞信不复存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/ubs-completes-historic-takeover-as-credit-suisse-ceases-to-exist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团完成了对其前竞争对手瑞士信贷的历史性收购，标志着瑞士金融业开启新篇章，因为该已倒闭的银行已正式不复存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/ubs-completes-historic-takeover-as-credit-suisse-ceases-to-exist</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 10:42:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本上月斥资创纪录的 620 亿美元支撑日元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/japan-spent-record-62-billion-in-past-month-on-yen-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日元兑美元汇率跌至 34 年来的最低点后，日本上个月花费了创纪录的 9.8 万亿日元（622 亿美元）来支撑日元，超过了 2022 年日本为捍卫日元所花费的总金额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/japan-spent-record-62-billion-in-past-month-on-yen-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 10:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
